ContactEntityType

This example value set defines a set of codes that can be used to indicate the purpose for which you would contact a contact party.

This value set defines it's own terms in the system http://hl7.org/fhir/contactentity-type

CodeDisplayDefinition
BILLBilling
ADMINAdministrative
HRHuman Resource
PAYORPayor
PATINFPatientGeneric information contact for patients
PRESSPress
